# Stage: contract — freeze the implementation contract

## Goal

Take the architecture-stage `contract-seed` (and any zod schemas + ADRs)
and FREEZE them: produce the final `contracts/*.ts` (zod schemas / tRPC
routers / TypeScript interfaces) that the implement stage will code
against without further negotiation.

This is the **G-c gate** in TOGAF terms: Architecture Contract. Once
frozen, contract is immutable until a new architecture stage_run is
opened.

